name: Dynamite
overview: A maze/labyrinth game published by Cascade Games/Cascade Software in their rather infamous Cassette 50 compilation (C64 version). This is a one player game and your mission is to rob the bank in a limited time and escape. You have to make your way through the invisible maze towards the safe. The fire button will show you a map of the maze, which you can view eight times. Good luck!
